# Momentum Builder™ Framework (T-012)

**Full document:** `docs/MOMENTUM_BUILDER_FRAMEWORK.md`

Momentum Builders™ are **not games**. Short (2–10 min) guided **practice** that strengthens real capabilities and connects to real business.

## Core question

> How will this make the member a stronger entrepreneur?

## Required spec fields

Primary capability · optional secondary · journey stages · Business Asset connection · Spark Card / Guild / Gallery when relevant · reflection question · practical application · EF support strategy · estimated time.

**Type:** `MomentumBuilderSpec` in `lib/sparkMomentumBuilders/types.ts`

## Flow

Arrival → Context → Challenge → Practice → Insight → Reflection → Business Application → Capability Growth → Connection

## Never

Childish · arcade-like · scores/leaderboards · winners · disconnected abstract exercises · manipulation.

## Celebrate instead

Insights · improved thinking · capability growth · business application. **Learning is the reward.**

## Growth levels (not Easy/Hard)

Explore™ · Practice™ · Apply™ · Master™

## Integration chain

```
Momentum Builder™ → Spark Card™ → Business Asset™ → Gallery™ → Guidance™
```

## EF standards

Immediate structure · low setup · pausable · no interruption penalty · ADHD-friendly.

## V1 note

`lib/momentumBuilders/` catalog is EF-reset subset today. New entrepreneurial Builders implement **this framework**.

Also: T-011 Spark Cards · T-010 journey (Build stage emphasis) · T-005 Pattern 5 Practice · T-007 resilience · T-015 Gallery (meaningful moments only) · T-016 Daily Discoveries.
